videos.description: Rob Gray lobs it up for Devin Davis who slams it down for Houston.
videos.headline: Gray connects with Davis for alley-oop

videos.description: Breaon Brady works his way around the defense and lays it in to extend Houston's lead.
videos.headline: Brady uses nice moves on lay-in

videos.description: Corey David Jr. drains a long 3-pointer giving the Cougars 12 3-pointers in the first half vs. ECU.
videos.headline: Houston stays hot from behind the arc

videos.description: Houston outscores ECU by 49 in the first half, which is the second-largest scoring margin in a half vs. a D-I team over the last 10 seasons.
videos.headline: Houston up by 49 at half vs. ECU

videos.description: Gabe Grant sinks a 3-pointer, giving the Cougars a season-high of 105 points with over four minutes left to play.
videos.headline: Houston showing no mercy in blowout of ECU
